#. Add-on summary/title, usually the user visible name of the add-on
#. Translators: Summary/title for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in add-on store
#: buildVars.py:21
msgid "Markdown Navigator"
msgstr "Markdown-навигатор"

#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-on store
#: buildVars.py:24
msgid ""
"An NVDA add-on that provides structured navigation (headings, lists, tables, "
"etc.) in editable text areas for Markdown files."
msgstr ""
"Дополнение для NVDA, обеспечивающее структурную навигацию (заголовки, "
"списки, таблицы и т.д.) в редактируемых текстовых областях для Markdown-"
"файлов."

